// In the House 1

title: Node_1
---
<<play_voice TylerNormal>>
Tyler: Hey man, welcome to the crib!

<<play_voice TylerNormal>>
Tyler: This is where I live! Pretty spaceous isn't it?

<<play_voice TylerNormal>>
Tyler: There's a suspicious amount of beds in the upper floor, you can pick any bed you want!

<<play_voice TylerNormal>>
Tyler:  I sleep in the basement... which is inacessible... so dont worry about taking my bed!

<<play_voice TylerNormal>>
Tyler: Take a look around, and once you're ready for adventure...

<<play_voice TylerNormal>>
Tyler: Come to me and we'll go do something!

<<play_voice TylerNormal>>
Tyler: Also... I know im kinda breaking the fourth wall...

<<play_voice TylerNormal>>
Tyler: But... do you want me to explain the controls?

-> Yeah, I'd like to know what buttons do what.
    <<play_voice TylerNormal>>
    Tyler: To interact with things you press E and you walk with WASD.
    <<play_voice TylerNormal>>
    Tyler: If you forget the controls you can pause the game with ESC and look there, I've written them there for you.
    <<play_voice TylerNormal>>
    Tyler: You can also press P, which stands for sPecial action... It's kinda funny, heh.
-> It's okay, I'm an expert!
    <<play_voice TylerNormal>>
    Tyler: Heh, I see how it is.

<<play_voice TylerNormal>>
Tyler: Okay, I wont break the fourth wall again, Promise.

<<play_voice TylerNormal>>
Tyler: Dont forget, once you're ready for action, come and talk to me okay?
<<nodeIndex 2>>
===

title: Node_2
---
<<play_voice TylerNormal>>
Tyler: So, you're ready for some action?
-> Yeah! let's go!
    <<play_voice TylerNormal>>
    Tyler: Isn't someone excited?
    <<play_voice TylerNormal>>
    Tyler: Let's go then, go out of the main door and I'll lead the way.
    <<nodeIndex 3>>
-> I'd like a bit more time here...
    <<play_voice TylerNormal>>
    Tyler: Okay, take your time, there's no rush.
