// Fat Stealing

title: Node_4
---
<<play_voice TylerNormal>>
Tyler: Hey, nice to see that you survived the drive!

<<play_voice TylerNormal>>
Tyler: Now, I'm kinda stationary here so, you'll need to do the work.

<<play_voice TylerNormal>>
Tyler: There's fat in the dumpsters in the back of the beauty clinic, go around and get that for me.

<<play_voice TylerNormal>>
Tyler: Search around the area for two Lye canisters, we need those too.

-> Okay, I'll get to it.
    <<play_voice TylerNormal>>
    Tyler: Yeah! that's the spirit!
-> Um... why do we need those two things?
    <<play_voice TylerNormal>>
    Tyler: You ask too many questions.
    <<play_voice TylerNormal>>
    Tyler: Once we get back to the crib I'll tell you.

<<play_voice TylerNormal>>
Tyler: Now, go and get to it.
<<nodeIndex 5>>
===

title: Node_5
---
-> I've got the things you asked for!
   <<if CheckFatHeist() == true>>
       Tyler: Perfect. You've got the fat and the lye. Let's get in the car.
       <<jump Start_Heist>>
   <<else>>
       Tyler: You're still missing some stuff. 
       Tyler: I need 2 tubs of fat and 2 bags of lye before we can move.
   <<endif>>
-> What do I need to do again?
    <<play_voice TylerNormal>>
    Tyler: You need to turn right by the entrance of the clinic and go around it to the back. 
    <<play_voice TylerNormal>>
    Tyler: There you'll find the fat that we need.
    <<play_voice TylerNormal>>
    Tyler: Around the area are two Lye canisters, we need those too.
    <<play_voice TylerNormal>>
    Tyler: So you need two fat and two lye canisters.
-> Why are we stealing fat?
    <<play_voice TylerNormal>>
    Tyler: You remember when we met... 
    <<play_voice TylerNormal>>
    Tyler: on the plane...
    <<play_voice TylerNormal>>
    Tyler: What did I have in that suitcase..?
